Reviews.Title: The best price
Reviews.Author: Donald
Reviews.Content: The best price, a good value for the money. This battery worked great, was delievered on time and as advertised.

Reviews.Title: There When I Need It!
Reviews.Author: KarenR
Reviews.Content: I always purchase computer batteries, chargers etc., through Amazon.  No fuss, no muss...always here on time and never had a problem and pricing if more than fair if you take the time to look.  Will continue to make my needed purchases.

Reviews.Title: The new DELL Battery does not solve the purpose
Reviews.Author: Amazon Customer
Reviews.Content: Even if we put the battery for 8 hours of charge, It is charging for only 95% and NOT CHARGING 100 PER CENT. However, I am not satisfied with the performance and the new DELL battery does not solve the purpose.
